"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Annual Meeting and Awards Dinner<\/strong> Each year the Beaver Dam Chamber &amp; Visitor Center recognizes organizations and individuals who are leaders in the community at an annual awards dinner. <a href=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/annual-awards\/\"><b>Learn more and submit an awards application.<\/b><\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-f79fc52 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"f79fc52\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-1170409\" data-id=\"1170409\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ff8f643 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ff8f643\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"229\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/EventLogo.BreakfastNetwork-300x229.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-4325\" alt=\"Beaver Dam Area Chamber of Commerce Presents - - Breakfast Network\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/EventLogo.BreakfastNetwork-300x229.jpg 300w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/EventLogo.BreakfastNetwork.jpg 420w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-31bfafb\" data-id=\"31bfafb\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-26ded1d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"26ded1d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Breakfast Network <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The second Tuesday every other month members are invited to a networking event. The Breakfast Network gives you the opportunity to network with other Chamber members and it provides you with learning opportunities that may help grow you, your business or our community.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-6fa9efd elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"6fa9efd\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-e3fbf25\" data-id=\"e3fbf25\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-95f8c43 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"95f8c43\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"229\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/MemberEvent.BusinessAfterHours-300x229.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-4052\" alt=\"Beaver Dam Chamber of Commerce Presents A Business After Hours\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/MemberEvent.BusinessAfterHours-300x229.jpg 300w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/MemberEvent.BusinessAfterHours.jpg 420w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-322c788\" data-id=\"322c788\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0acfdd5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0acfdd5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Business After Hours<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is typically held the third Wednesday of the month. Members are invited to a business for networking and refreshments. It is an opportunity to connect and learn more about a business or organization. <\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-551ad9d elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"551ad9d\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-31f4db4\" data-id=\"31f4db4\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-76c75a2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"76c75a2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"229\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/MemberEvent.BusinessPowerHour-300x229.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-4053\" alt=\"Business Power Hour logo\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/MemberEvent.BusinessPowerHour-300x229.jpg 300w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/MemberEvent.BusinessPowerHour.jpg 420w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8405b18\" data-id=\"8405b18\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-001ba5e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"001ba5e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Business Power Hour <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">is a one-hour virtual presentation over lunch that will cover a wide range of topics from Google training and grant opportunities to economic forecasts and leadership development and everything in between. Business Power Hours are typically held once a month on varying days depending on presenter availability.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2f59ae3 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"2f59ae3\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-1ed5f89\" data-id=\"1ed5f89\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1486f16 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1486f16\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"225\" height=\"225\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/women-in-business.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17139\" alt=\"Women in Business\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/women-in-business.png 225w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/women-in-business-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-00c3af6\" data-id=\"00c3af6\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6d07518 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6d07518\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"141\" data-end=\"837\">The Beaver Dam Chamber &amp; Visitor Center\u2019s <strong>Women in Business<\/strong> events are held several times throughout the year and are open to the public. Each gathering is designed to bring women together to connect, learn, and grow\u2014both professionally and personally. Events typically feature a guest speaker or expert covering topics such as leadership, financial planning, mental health, and more. Attendees also have the opportunity to network and build meaningful relationships with other women in the community. Whether you&#8217;re an entrepreneur, business professional, or community leader, Women in Business offers a welcoming space to be inspired, gain valuable insights, and expand your network.<\/p><p data-start=\"839\" data-end=\"898\">Check our events calendar for upcoming dates and details.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-5a9df07 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"5a9df07\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-24b5842\" data-id=\"24b5842\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6867422 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"6867422\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"229\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/EventLogo.BDConnect-300x229.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-4326\" alt=\"BD Connect logo\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/EventLogo.BDConnect-300x229.jpg 300w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/EventLogo.BDConnect.jpg 420w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cf96570\" data-id=\"cf96570\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-874b4a4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"874b4a4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>BD Connect <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">is a social networking group for adults 21-40ish who live or work in the Dodge County area and are looking for ways to expand their social and professional circles.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">BD Connect meets monthly hosting different types of networking events. Participants will engage in social, charitable and professional events that not only have a community impact, but also a personal impact.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div