ass=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-size: 1em;\">T<\/span><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-size: 1em;\">ee off with the Beaver Dam Chamber &amp; Visitor Center at the <b>Annual Chamber Golf Outing,<\/b> a highlight of the summer! Typically held on the last Monday in June, this exciting event alternates between two premier locations: Old Hickory Golf Club (even years) and the Beaver Dam Country Club (odd years). Don\u2019t miss this opportunity to network, enjoy a day on the course, and support our community. Visit our\u00a0<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/community-events\/#cid=1829&amp;wid=701\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">events calendar<\/a><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-size: 1em;\">\u00a0for more details!<\/span><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-size: 1em;\">\u00a0<\/span><b style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-size: 1em;\">Event is open to all &#8211; <a href=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/community-events\/#id=2616&amp;cid=1829&amp;wid=701\">sign up now<\/a>!\u00a0 Otherwise, <a href=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/2026-Golf-Outing-Golfers-Sponsor-Registration-Form.pdf\">download the forms<\/a> and mail in your registration.<\/b><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-01500cd elementor-section-boxe